details.text: Coding has no system. A code with no system has no defined meaning, and it cannot be validated. A system should be provided

None of the codings provided are in the value set 'LibraryType' (http://hl7.org/fhir/ValueSet/library-type|4.0.1), and a coding should come from this value set unless it has no suitable code (note that the validator cannot judge what is suitable) (codes = null#model-definition)
